      "side": 1,
      "message": "I would reword this.\n\n\"\"\"\nWhen using ambient capabilities, CAP_SET{GID,UID} can be inherited across execve(2), so SECBIT_KEEP_CAPS is not strictly needed. Still, attempt to set it unless it is locked (which can happen if we\u0027re using Minijail in an already-jailed process).",
